conference#Conference_participant: The conferenceparticipant is the child of the conferencecontributor, the activeconferenceparticipant is the child of the invited speaker and the passiveconferenceparticipant is the parent of the conferencecontributor.
conference#Active_conference_participant: The activeconferenceparticipant is the parent of the conferencecontributor, the regularauthor and the invitedspeaker. The activeconferenceparticipant is the equivalent of the conferenceparticipant and the parent of the passiveconferenceparticipant.
conference#Passive_conference_participan: The conferenceparticipant is the parent of the activeconferenceparticipant. The conferencecontributor is the child of the invited speaker and the conferenceparticipant is the child of the conferenceparticipant.
conference#Person: The parent of a conferenceparticipant is the reviewer. The activeconferenceparticipant is the equivalent of the passiveconferenceparticipant. The committee member is the parent of the organizer and the committee member is the parent of the committee. The invitedspeaker is the parent of the activeconferenceparticipant and the trackworkshopchair is the parent of the conferencecontributor.
conference#Review_expertise: Reviewexpertise is a child of Thing.
conference#Submitted_contribution: The submittedcontribution is the parent of the reviewedcontribution, which is equivalent to the rejectedcontribution. It is also the child of the writtencontribution, which is equivalent to the conferencecontribution. It is the parent of the presentation, which is the parent of the invitedtalk and is the child of the poster.
conference#Reviewer: The reviewer is a child of the person who is the parent of the conference applicant. The registeered applicant is the parent of the paid applicant and the conference applicant is the parent of the conference applicant.
conference#Regular_author: Regularauthor is the parent of contribution1author and contributioncoauthor. The activeconferenceparticipant is the child of invitedspeaker and conferencecontributor.
conference#Conference_contributor: The conferencecontributor is the parent of the conferenceapplicant, the registeeredapplicant, the paidapplicant and the activeconferenceparticipant. The activeconferenceparticipant is the child of the conferencecontributor and the regularauthor is the parent of contribution1author.
conference#Contribution_1th-author: The contribution1author is the child of the regularauthor and the conferencecontributor. The activeconferenceparticipant is the parent of the conferencecontributor.
conference#Contribution_co-author: Contributioncoauthor is the child of regularauthor and the parent of contribution1author.
conference#Conference_contribution: The conferencecontribution is the parent of the conferencedocument and the informationforparticipants. It is also the parent of the poster, the invitedtalk and the writtencontribution.
conference#Co-chair: The chair of a trackworkshop is the child of a committee member and a parent of a trackworkshopchair.
conference#Committee: The committee is the parent of the steeringcommittee and the programcommittee. It is the equivalent of the organizingcommittee.
conference#Committee_member: The committee member is the parent of the chair and the chair. The committee member is also the parent of the organizer and the child of the organization. The committee member is the parent of the conference applicant and the late paid applicant.
conference#Abstract: The extendedabstract is a child of the regularcontribution which is parented to the submittedcontribution. The writtencontribution is also a child of the extendedabstract.
conference#Extended_abstract: Extendedabstract is equivalent to regularcontribution. Writtencontribution is parented to reviewedcontribution and submittedcontribution is parented to submittedcontribution.
conference#Invited_speaker: invitedspeaker is a child of the conferencecontributor and the trackworkshopchair. He is also a child of the regularauthor and contributioncoauthor.
conference#Information_for_participants: Informationforparticipants is a child of conferencedocument which is parented by conferenceannouncement.
conference#Conference_document: The conferencedocument is the parent of conferenceannouncement and informationforparticipants. It is also the parent of conferencecontribution which is equivalent to poster and regularcontribution which is equivalent to paper.
conference#Organization: The parent of the organizer is the parent of the committee member who is a child of the committee member and the reviewer.
conference#Regular_contribution: The paper is the parent of the extendedabstract which is the parent of the abstract. The paper is the parent of the conference contribution and the written contribution is the child of the regularcontribution.
conference#Poster: The poster is the parent of the writtencontribution and the submittedcontribution. The conferencecontribution is the child of the conferencedocument and is the parent of the review.
conference#Written_contribution: The writtencontribution is the child of conferencecontribution, which is the parent of the call for participation. It is also the child of poster and reviewedcontribution. It is the parent of acceptedcontribution and camerareadycontribution.
conference#Conference_applicant: The conference applicant is the child of a person who is the parent of a reviewer. The registeered applicant is the parent of the paid applicant and the earlypaid applicant.
conference#Camera_ready_contribution: The camerareadycontribution is a child of the acceptedcontribution and the reviewedcontribution.
conference#Accepted_contribution: The acceptedcontribution is the parent of the camerareadycontribution and the reviewedcontribution is the parent of the rejectedcontribution.
conference#Program_committee: The programcommittee is the child of the committee and the parent of the steeringcommittee.
conference#Organizing_committee: The organizingcommittee is a child of the committee which is equivalent to the programcommittee.
conference#Steering_committee: The steeringcommittee is equivalent to the committee and the organizingcommittee.
conference#Conference_volume: conferencevolume is a child of conference.
conference#Conference: The conference is the parent of conferencevolume.
conference#Call_for_paper: The callforpaper is a child of conferencedocument which is parented by conferencecontribution. The poster is also parented by conferencecontribution. The written contribution is also a child of conferencecontribution and regular contribution.
conference#Conference_announcement: The conference announcement is a child of the conferencedocument which is parented by the informationforparticipants.
conference#Paper: The paper is equivalent to the regularcontribution which is the child of the writtencontribution and the poster. The conferencecontribution is the child of conferencedocument which is parented by conferencewww.
conference#Invited_talk: The invitedtalk is the child of the presentation. The conferencecontribution is the parent of the poster, the submittedcontribution is the parent of the acceptedcontribution and the reviewedcontribution is the parent of the acceptedcontribution.
conference#Conference_part: The conferencepart is the parent of the workshop and the tutorial.
conference#Presentation: The conferencecontribution is the parent of the writtencontribution which is the child of the poster. It is also the parent of the invitedtalk.
conference#Chair: The chair of the committee is the child of the committee member and the parent of the conference contributor.
conference#Track: The track is a child of conferencepart which is the parent of tutorial.
conference#Workshop: The workshop is the child of conferencepart which is the parent of track.
conference#Tutorial: The tutorial is child of conferencepart which is parent of track.
conference#Rejected_contribution: The rejectedcontribution is a child of the reviewedcontribution and the submittedcontribution.
conference#Reviewed_contribution: The submittedcontribution and the acceptedcontribution are both children of conferencecontribution. The conferencecontribution is the parent of the call for participation and the reviewedcontribution is the parent of the rejectedcontribution. The writtencontribution is the child of the submittedcontribution and the acceptedcontribution is the parent of the camerareadycontribution.
conference#Review: The conferencedocument is the parent of conferenceannouncement and is the child of conferencedocument.
conference#Late_paid_applicant: The latepaid applicant is the child of the paid applicant and the parent of the earlypaid applicant.
conference#Paid_applicant: The paid applicant is the child of the registeered applicant and the conference applicant. The reviewer is the parent of the paid applicant and the late paid applicant is the parent of the early paid applicant.
conference#Early_paid_applicant: The latepaid applicant is the parent of the paid applicant.
conference#Organizer: The child of the organizer is the child of the organization Thing and the committee member is the parent of the chair.
conference#Call_for_participation: The callforparticipation is a child of the conferencedocument which is the parent of the informationforparticipants.
conference#Registeered_applicant: The registeeredapplicant is the parent of the paidapplicant, the latepaidapplicant and the conferenceapplicant. The trackworkshopchair is also the parent of the registeeredapplicant.
conference#Track-workshop_chair: The trackworkshopchair is the child of the person who is the parent of the reviewer.
conference#Conference_www: conferencewww is the child of conferencedocument which is the parent of review.
conference#Review_preference: reviewpreference is a child of Thing.
